        "gg-WuHZWR1w_text": "<p>The truth is, no skincare routine is complete without collagen support that actually reaches the deeper layers. If you’re ready to give your skin what it’s truly been asking for—start with Nifora’s 5-in-1 Collagen Capsule.</p>",
        "gg2z2PW3lzQ_text": "<p>Trusted by 40,000+ women</p>",
        "gg480sgH-Nc_text": "You’ve done the creams. You’ve done the serums. Now it’s time to work from within.",
        "gg4jz0I1VwM_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://223a18-2.myshopify.com/cdn/shop/files/gempages_560737037540394069-71051f67-8e75-4fa8-b548-3d16cd73cd7a.png?v=1706493534710474793",
