        "checksum": "f567214973e5b8191a709c4233736dfbdf392c7318441791f93ad2f564e57043_1_1_1_0__1",
        "gg1IqMe2L0w_text": "<p>With every capsule, she’s not trying to look 25—<strong>she’s fueling vitality, strength, and balance from the inside out</strong>. It’s for the woman who wants to keep showing up for her life, her way—no filters, no fluff. Just something that helps her feel like&nbsp;herself again.</p>",
        "gg3vGvIMqvd_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/7_3.png",
        "ggSTMMh343s_text": "<p>That’s why people love this capsule. It’s easy, quick, and totally mess-free. Just one step, and you’re done. Because <strong>real results come from consistency</strong>—and that starts with something you’ll actually&nbsp;want to stick with.</p>",
        "ggczeYX6lJK_text": "6. You’ll Feel It—Not Just See It.",
        "ggd6agp_vR8_text": "5. No Mixing. No Weird Taste. Just One Easy Step.",
        "ggdagC8BRQM_text": "<p>A lot of women say they start noticing changes <strong>after just a few weeks</strong>—less joint stiffness, stronger nails, fuller hair, and skin that actually feels smoother and more supple.</p>",
        "ggkYRDX_hyI_text": "<p>Let’s be real—most collagen products are kind of a hassle. Powders that clump, drinks that taste weird, or routines that feel like a full-time job. <strong>For busy women, it’s just not sustainable.</strong></p>",
        "ggkmtPJdmK0_text": "7. It Supports the Whole You.",
        "ggmUMHmlfzt_text": "<p>It’s not magic—<strong>it’s the body finally getting what it needs to rebuild from within</strong>. Unlike creams that rinse off at the end of the day, this kind of support sticks with you. The results show up in the mirror, sure—but even more in how you&nbsp;feel day to day. <strong>More comfort. More confidence. More energy to show up as yourself.</strong></p>",
        "ggt5trgs_C5_text": "<p>This isn’t just another beauty fix—<strong>it’s a daily wellness tool designed with&nbsp;real women in mind</strong>. It supports the full picture of aging: physical changes, hormonal shifts, and everything in between.</p>",
        "ggtgOPwLJpH_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/6_3.png",
        "gguwVXNczy-_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/5_3.png"
      },
      "type": "gp-section-626145920165216819"
    },
    "gp_section_626145920181862963": {
      "settings": {
        "checksum": "ac77f1a9e6a83679b6f4f2cc8b8f472c3ef8b3e9936050d9449dcfcd528a9432_1_1_1_0__1",
        "gg26i4zU6M9_text": "3. Menopause Changes Everything and Your Routine Should Too.",
        "gg2YeuZSDLG_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/4_3.png",
        "gg4Cc7NeQu0_text": "<p>It’s especially perfect for women in their 30s, 40s, and beyond, when collagen production naturally starts to decline <strong>(yep, up to 1% less each year after 25!)</strong>. That loss can show up as wrinkles, joint stiffness, or thinning hair.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>This capsule helps fill in those gaps—<strong>so you can feel as strong, radiant, and confident as ever.</strong></p>",
        "gg59Q6qkpGD_text": "<p>Most formulas skip these, <strong>but this one covers all the bases.</strong> When the body gets everything it needs—not just one piece of the puzzle—<strong>you really start to see the difference.</strong> Think of it like giving your skin a full renovation, not just a quick fix.</p>",
        "gg6uIDISuu8_text": "1. It’s Not Just One Collagen, It’s Five.",
        "gg96ugxQo9g_text": "<p>That’s why I’m so glad <strong>this formula doesn’t just stop at collagen.</strong> It also includes hormone-supportive ingredients like magnesium and biotin, which help my body adjust instead of fight the changes. It’s not about stopping menopause—<strong>it’s about working&nbsp;with it and still feeling strong, glowy, and like myself.</strong></p>",
        "gg9mt8SYjhb_text": "<p>Let’s be real—no one wants to juggle five different supplements every day. That’s why people are loving Nifora’s Multi-Collagen Capsule. It combines <strong>Types I, II, III, V, and X</strong> to support skin, joints, bones, and more—<strong>all in one easy daily dose.</strong></p>",
        "ggAnsGbE4zn_text": "<p>Here’s the thing: <strong>collagen doesn’t work solo</strong>. That’s why this capsule includes essentials like vitamin C <strong>(which helps your body actually&nbsp;make collagen)</strong>, plus keratin and biotin to support strong hair, nails, and smoother skin.</p>",
        "ggEJn8C1uIW_text": "<p>I used to think dryness and sagging just meant I needed a richer moisturizer. But turns out, it goes way deeper than that. As we age, our skin’s support system—<strong>collagen</strong>—starts breaking down. And no cream can fix that from the outside.</p>",
        "ggI2ohkC2hm_text": "<p>That’s why I started taking collagen supplements, and honestly, <strong>it made a huge difference.</strong> It’s not just about that glow (though that’s a bonus!)—<strong>it’s about rebuilding the foundation so your skin stays strong, plump, and bouncy for the long haul.</strong></p>",
        "ggIh9jAl7hW_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/1_4.png",
        "ggLcRQHLYyO_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/3_3.png",
        "ggMTtLiPXuX_text": "<p>By Rachel Beaumont | July 2025</p>",
        "ggUYRw8nmHu_text": "7 Smart Reasons Why 40,000+ Women Are Switching to Multi-Collagen Capsules Instead of Traditional Skincare",
        "gghkAsN-NAk_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/2_3.png",
        "ggntnhoAX_p_text": "4. It Includes Ingredients That Help Collagen Work.",
        "ggsLvG4OII__text": "2. Your Skin Doesn’t Just Need Moisture. It Needs Structure.",
        "ggsdxtqBRbP_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/00.jpg",
        "ggsxyDLVOcJ_text": "<p>No one really warned me <strong>how much hormones could affect my skin and joints</strong>—until I started feeling it. When estrogen dips, collagen takes a hit too, and suddenly things feel thinner, stiffer, and just… off.</p>",
        "gguCnwVa854_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://223a18-2.myshopify.com/cdn/shop/files/gempages_560737037540394069-8130e07f-f531-4cb2-82be-c58746eb4e38.png?v=12469724417750347875",
